<div class="col-sm-12 col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">

  <p class="content-type-label text-center">FDA News Release</p>
  <h1 class="content-title text-center">Coronavirus (COVID-19) Update: FDA Issues Emergency Use Authorization for Potential COVID-19 Treatment</h1>

  
  <div class="lcds-toolbar lcds-toolbar--social">
      <ul class="lcds-share lcds-share--default">
